Ano mám to.

344
00:16:38,040 --> 00:16:39,030
Je vyprodáno,je mi líto.

345
00:16:39,030 --> 00:16:39,500
Vyprodáno?

346
00:16:39,500 --> 00:16:40,130
Vyprodáno.

347
00:16:40,130 --> 00:16:40,900
Vyprodáno?

348
00:16:40,900 --> 00:16:42,030
Vyprodáno.

349
00:16:54,250 --> 00:16:55,700
Achchchch!

350
00:16:55,700 --> 00:16:56,640
Hm?

351
00:16:56,640 --> 00:16:58,260
Sensei,co to děláte?

352
00:16:58,260 --> 00:16:59,350
Co...?

353
